snippet.textDisplay:
These burgers and sandwiches don't look like the ones I have in my northern Texas stores. Those look pale and greasy and kinda gross. Well for one you needed to use the ketchup because the fries are made to go with the custom ketchup. I am a condiment whore, but I use very little of the ketchup because it is perfect. I know people love salty things, but I sincerely appreciate how it cuts down on the salt on the fries, I don't have a shower of salt from my fingers after every fry.
Also, so sorry you didn't get to get the Buffalo Ranch Chicken Strip Sandwich with pickles added to it and a Dr. Pepper shake with chocolate added to it.
